title: Star pitchers set for Astros at Yankees, Cubs at Pirates wild-card games
text: Baseball Houston Astros ace pitcher Dallas Keuchel twice dominated the New York Yankees this season and will now be relied on to pitch the game of his life, while starting on three days’ rest for the first time in his career.
